7.24.25  8:26 pm   When I retire in 2 years, one of my goals is to learn a 2nd language. What is your process for learning a new language? Do you have any tips you can share with me?

      what you wanna do is find video content you enjoy. i always prefer genuine speaking content. not lesson content, not read content, not scripted content. best case scenario is you can find genuine talking content that has been transcribed accurately. and then just start playing games with this content

7.24.25  8:37 am   do your songs lyrics tend to be reflections of what your thinking/ an idea you want to explore, or are they more like word association, going from one pleasing sound to the next, with the thematic connection not as much of a focus? And in general, what is your songwriting process?

      the most important thing to remember here is the lyrics are not separate from the melodies and harmony that they go with. just as the left half of a golf ball is usually not separate from the right half of the golf ball
